Apt. 7, Minneapolis, MN   55403', 'For more information or to view this apartment please contact the building caretaker, Greg, at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Pictures are not from this apartment but are from a similar one in the building.', '$955.00/month', 'Utilities included in Rent: heat, trash removal, gas for the range', 'Residents pay electricity, water/sewer, cable/internet.', 'KEY FEATURES:', '-Bedrooms: 1BR', '-Bathrooms:  1 Bath', '-Hardwood floors', '-Square', 'Footage:  575 square feet', '-Second Floor of building', '-Lease', 'Duration:  1 Year.', ' 6 and 9 month lease options available for an additional fee', '-Deposit:  $500', '-Pets Policy:  Up to two cats allowed with additional deposit and monthly fee.', '-Laundry:  Shared', 'A Hornig Companies community     -     Apply online at <URL>', "Come home to this beautiful 1920s era brownstone in an absolutely fantastic Lowry Hill location with Sebastian Joe's  just down the block.", 'Lake of the Isles and all of Uptown are within walking distance.', "You'll love the hardwood floors and their bright warm spaces with vintage details.", 'The common areas have been recently updated making this building a real gem.']
